node.text:
Together with @volkswagen.wedrivefootball we brought Michal, 2021 champion of the #FCBayern U17 Freestyle Tournament, to Munich. 🎁👏 

Check out his amazing skills at FC Bayern World, Marienplatz and many more spots around the city. ⚽🤯

node.title: U17 Freestyle Tournament 2021 Winner Michal visits Munich 📍🤩
